Global Refrigerated Storage Tank Market Insights
Refrigerated Storage Tank Market size was valued at USD 6.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% from 2024 to 2030.

Refrigerated Storage Tank Market Overview
The global refrigerated storage tank market is projected to reach a market value of USD 7.5 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.1% from 2023 to 2030. The demand for refrigerated storage tanks has significantly increased due to the rising consumption of perishable goods, such as food and beverages, pharmaceuticals, and chemicals, which require controlled temperatures for preservation. The market is expected to expand as advancements in tank insulation and cooling technologies continue to improve energy efficiency, contributing to the overall market growth.

